# MISSION 05

All information: [main campaign information](https://github.com/OFCRA/templates/blob/master/campaigns/37-mangusta/mangusta.IslaDuala3/README.md)  
Any other question: contact Galevsky

# Sitac & Weather

Following the American assault on Pumado Base in the north of the island. The command of the Russian forces decided to launch an offensive on the town of Kinsella. The US embassy in the city center is a prime target for destabilizing Swazili region. A high ranking officer is a post west of the city in a well-protected military complex. Its elimination could force the US military to withdraw from the city.

Mission start time: 16h00 loc.  
Duration: 2h  
Fog: none 
Ceiling: medium  
Cloud cover: 4/8  
Forecast: stable


# Task Orders

## USA specific Objectives

**Protect Officer (5 pts)** 

The US Army officer is stationed in a military complex west of the town of Kinsella. Its survival is essential for the continuation of operations in the region.

![obj](http://img11.hostingpics.net/pics/370476201612251953391.jpg)

*Victory condition:* US Army must protect the officer until the end of the mission.

## Russia specific Objectives

**Kill Officer (5 pts)** 

We know that a US Army officer is stationed in a military complex west of the town of Kinsella. It is a priority target for Russia and its elimination to weaken the opponent considerably.

![obj](http://img11.hostingpics.net/pics/218691201612251952251.jpg)

*Victory condition:* The Russians must eliminate the officer before the end of the mission.

## Common Objectives

-

# Capture Area

**Capture US Ambassy (3 pts)**  

The US Embassy is a prime target for the Russians. The Top Secret documents are always mine of very important information for the enemy.

![obj](http://img11.hostingpics.net/pics/825942201612251953041.jpg)

*Victory condition:* at the very end of the 2-hours long mission, units inside the area (accurate boundaries displayed on map) are counted, and the points go to the side who has at least 1 player more than the other side. No points taken if no one in zone.
